{"tid":1085692,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"樂壇新人黑氣石譚詠麟勉勵MIRROR要堅持","createTime":"2019-03-31T10:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T05:53:17.000Z","uid":32081,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4660916ab794ace87eac3b143f6786e63581eef6","tid":1085692,"uid":32081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T10:45:05.000Z","msg":"譚詠麟叫MIRROR堅持<br />\n<br />\n譚詠麟（校長）和男團MIRROR昨日在西九文化區出席起步禮，MIRROR向來粉絲多，連校長也有留意，他寄語新一代要捱得，皆因娛樂圈千變萬化，即使遇到不快事都不要放棄、不要怕蝕底。<br />\n<br />\n談及ViuTV將製作《全民造星》新一輯，校長說：「一定係咁，娛樂圈係要一代換一代。」問他會否叫世姪參與？他笑說：「我啲世姪嘅年紀都幾大吓。」MIRROR隊長Lokman表示已有朋友報名參加，《全民造星》監製花姐說：「計劃5月開始面試，因為我哋預計今年多人過上年，參加者要18歲以上，今年一樣有99強先，再分六、七個回合，最後就決賽選冠軍。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190331/20645511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190331%2F20645511&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP9%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=6a331fa8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190331%2F20645511&h=c0696585\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190331/20645511</a>"},{"pid":"c80f5f76dc5f13c63b9bcb5407d547ee8d768fc6","tid":1085692,"uid":172464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T10:45:55.000Z","msg":"唔該哂校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"776676e0336c197b6ae7249318eda1d8c4ca6ba7","tid":1085692,"uid":243531,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T10:50:19.000Z","msg":"MIRROR 收得皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067f6b706eba71481356260a32f652309944c369","tid":1085692,"uid":227420,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"776676e0336c197b6ae7249318eda1d8c4ca6ba7","tid":1085692,"uid":243531,"like":2,"disli